{"tid":387872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本SOD產既最強戰車原來已經進軍歐洲！","createTime":"2017-09-05T03:50:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T14:19:54.000Z","uid":25424,"like":214,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"815fb3420edc185009431266068d57365840048c","tid":387872,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T03:50:30.000Z","msg":"SOD魔鏡號駛往歐洲　尋獲素人洋妞啪啪啪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日本AV大廠「SOD」（Soft On Demand），曾用「魔鏡號」拍攝過無數動作片，而這次拍攝地點踏出日本，前往歐洲找外國素人啪啪啪了！<br />\nSOD在推特發文指出，這次魔鏡號前往歐洲，耗時182天在歐洲挑選願意演出的素人，在經過當地的工作人員向254位民眾搭訕後，挑出符合日本人口味的6位正妹拍片，讓粉絲看看正統的洋槍打洋妞，片子也於日前發售。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170904/640_af9da61c7b14a3a971c36e5483b4ba04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170904%2F640_af9da61c7b14a3a971c36e5483b4ba04.jpg&h=deccf4f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170904/640_1ce210d1b568335d3776849093881f9d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170904%2F640_1ce210d1b568335d3776849093881f9d.jpg&h=2d106bfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSeed 呀！"},{"pid":"672f88c9f501eed0885c8a4faa1949d99a175086","tid":387872,"uid":60404,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T03:51:11.000Z","msg":"SEED"},{"pid":"beb8817dba9eec9441d075bfaa6a5100e2b28fcf","tid":387872,"uid":7628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T03:51:34.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"5edbbda83c141d4152b9e219d883337e0bb84cd4","tid":387872,"uid":7840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T03:51:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7c9c0236ef89b291ea565f4d9525d7f69afeb5b5","tid":387872